data.description: Looking for life in the country?  Well, look no more!  Enjoy this 4 Bedroom and 2.5 Bath home situated on 1.26 acres.  Located out Central Ave in Brantley but with a Waycross address.  Brick home with spacious rooms, Large Kitchen and Vaulted Ceiling in the Great Room.  Enjoy the wood beams and brick fireplace.  There are 3 bedrooms on the right end of the home and 2 Baths.  The 4th bedroom and half bath are located on the left end near the garage-ideal for college aged person or in-law suite.  There is a single garage on the front of the house plus another garage on the rear that has a single garage door but additional work space and separate entry.  The lot is beautifully landscaped with grape vine, jasmine, fruit trees and lots of perennials.  The stainless steel range(1 year old) and refrigerator(2 yrs old) and a brand new dishwasher!  This property is in great condition so it will qualify for all types of financing.  Call quick, it won't last long.
